dc_description_s: This is the final deliverable for the Version 4 Statewide Parcel Map Database Project (V4). This feature class represents a comprehensive, spatially referenced collection of parcel geometries as recognized by local-level governments within the State of Wisconsin (the feature class is aggregated from county level and municipal-level data). See the V4 Project Homepage for more detail on the parameters for how data was prepared and submitted to this project: https://www.sco.wisc.edu/parcels/submission/.Schema documentation can be found within this feature class metadata and here: https://www.sco.wisc.edu/parcels/data/assets/V4/V4_Wisconsin_Statewide_Parcels_Schema_Documentation.pdf.Change log and known issues can be found here: https://www.sco.wisc.edu/parcels/data/assets/Wisconsin_Statewide_Parcels_Change_Log.pdf.
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
